headline: Sophisticated Resources to Support High-Net-Worth Clients Draws Advisor with $100 Million to Ameriprise Team
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 11, 2024--Q5 Wealth Management, a team of five financial advisors managing $1.5 billion in client assets in Houston and Beaumont, Texas, recently expanded with the addition of financial advisor Scott Guptill, CFA. Q5 joined the independent channel of Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) in August 2024 after a successful transition from UBS Financial Services, Inc. with a desire to significantly grow their practice by leveraging the sophisticated resources at Ameriprise. headline: Ameriprise Financial Named a Military Friendly® Employer for the Eleventh Consecutive Year
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 11, 2024--Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) today announced it was named a 2025 Military Friendly® Employer by VIQTORY, an organization that connects the military community to civilian employment and educational opportunities. This is the eleventh consecutive year Ameriprise has earned the distinction in recognition of its commitment and work to creating an inclusive and supportive work environment for military community members.
